{"tid":2381209,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際奧委會指責意大利政府干預體育 擬禁止東京奧運掛國旗及播國歌","createTime":"2021-01-26T11:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T10:30:21.000Z","uid":18692,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6551e119e0245f429d3e35fa90f805eeaa396daf","tid":2381209,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9b80K5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9b80K5.jpg&h=384d2877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果週三（1月27日）前，意大利政府干預意大利奧委會（CONI）的爭端仍未解決，國際奧委會（IOC）將於會議落實禁止在東京奧運會上懸掛意大利國旗以及播放意大利國歌。  <br />\n<br />\n2019年8月，意大利國會通過修改體育法的草案，由於涉嫌「政治干涉體育」引起國際奧委會不滿。草案授權政府組織奧林匹克體育賽事，包括計劃將CONI的經費從4億歐元大幅削減至僅4千萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n意大利報章《晚郵報》（Corriere Della Sera）披露一封由IOC負責與各國奧委會聯絡的官員James Macleod的信件。他警告孔特總理的內閣不要對CONI施加影響。<br />\n<br />\nIOC甚至威脅，「如果有關國家的憲法、法律或其他規定阻礙國家奧委會的行動，該國的奧委會將有可能被除名。」<br />\n<br />\n如果在今年東京奧運會上禁止意大利國旗和國歌，待遇將與因興奮劑醜聞被罰的俄羅斯相同。  <br />\n<br />\n2016年奧運會，意大利收獲8金12銀8銅，排名第9，較西班牙、澳洲和巴西高。<br />\n<br />\n近日前總理倫齊領導的意大利活力黨（Italia Viva），退出聯合政府，令執政聯盟失去國會多數席位，引發政治危機。總理孔特在國會的信任投票，參議院未獲絕對多數議席，代表他制訂或落實任何政策時，都會舉步維艱。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.herald.co.zw/ioc-threaten-italy-with-tokyo-2020-flag-and-anthem-ban-due-to-government-interference/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.herald.co.zw%2Fioc-threaten-italy-with-tokyo-2020-flag-and-anthem-ban-due-to-government-interference%2F&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv60GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=ed50c6c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.herald.co.zw/ioc-threaten-italy-with-tokyo-2020-flag-and-anthem-ban-due-to-government-interference/</a>"},{"pid":"d065e33af86f3822c81ca717fe43eadc425992d2","tid":2381209,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uu8LioxsX5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Duu8LioxsX5g&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv60GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=a900eef1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uu8LioxsX5g</a><br />\n意大利國歌"},{"pid":"7f18ddcea65991971948b5139779383eb6c177a9","tid":2381209,"uid":255980,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"咁中國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a22212951e0e6310126e14a16934ea70ef63c57","tid":2381209,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8103a754230e558dafc08b0389c0657c203acdb","tid":2381209,"uid":4964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7f18ddcea65991971948b5139779383eb6c177a9","tid":2381209,"uid":255980,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"咁中國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:40:09.000Z","msg":"可能有出幼幼,所以冇事"},{"pid":"775fbbd31785f6fc8df484bd9029824f0fd4fd9f","tid":2381209,"uid":104138,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"呢d 垃圾組織廢既"},{"pid":"bfa2d1026e38a4de76c8bbc7e1031e3d3ab76133","tid":2381209,"uid":9104,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"意大利: 搞到東京奧運會先同我講野啦"},{"pid":"d7e76f953434a2b0d05815e4aa2503c657cd0c4a","tid":2381209,"uid":136431,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"政府干預體育就要Ban<br />\n支那直頭政府指揮體育喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e8542bdf5e2749c8f7c368d039808a56c720db","tid":2381209,"uid":183758,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6